OWENS v. WARDEN OF MARYLAND PENITENTIARY [App. No. 94,

September Term, 1965.]

Decided February 15, 1966.

Before Hammond, Horney, Oppenheimer, Barnes and McWilliams, JJ. ’

Per Curiam.

Application for leave to appeal is denied for the reasons set out in the opinion of Judge Cullen in the lower court.

Application denied.
